text: Emilia Ramboldt, earlier Emilia Andersson, born 31 August 1988 in Sollentuna, Sweden) is a Swedish female ice hockey defencewoman. She played for Sweden during the women's ice hockey tournament during the 2010 Olympic Winter Games. ==Awards and honors== * 2008–09 MSU Mavericks Rookie of the YearMinnesota State Mavericks – Mavericks Announce 2008–09 Team Awards ==References== ==Other websites== * Swedish Olympic Commitee - Emilia Andersson Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm Category:Swedish ice hockey defencemen Category:Ice hockey defencemen
